The S3 URL of the file that defines the categories used to label the data objects. 
The file is a JSON structure in the following format: 
{ 
 "document-version": "2018-11-28" 
 "labels": [ 
 { 
 "label": "label 1" 
 }, 
 { 
 "label": "label 2" 
 }, 
 ... 
 { 
 "label": "label n" 
 } 
 ] 
}

